{"tid":1352740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警黑合作，主角係警，要滅嘅唔係牛屎佬","createTime":"2019-07-22T23:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T07:14:30.000Z","uid":223260,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"038145b602edb6ff3b0eaaa217dcf6f9024efe76","tid":1352740,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:32:17.000Z","msg":"你好嬲，你以為牛屎佬打你咩？唔係囉，要打人殺人（物理上）非常容易，問題係呢個世界有差佬，差佬有調查能力。當差佬同牛屎佬合作，佢先可以打得咁開心。<br />\n<br />\n我講過好都次敵人最強嘅武器係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">調查能力</span></span><br />\n所以要滅嘅，唔係牛屎佬。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ffa41c283c914c60271707c8686413510881a0bb","tid":1352740,"uid":272976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:35:51.000Z","msg":"唔好亂講，兩邊都要清算<br />\n愧對嗰句光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"36210f820163764650220f2f5bb84441b742b4d5","tid":1352740,"uid":3775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ffa41c283c914c60271707c8686413510881a0bb","tid":1352740,"uid":272976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:35:51.000Z","msg":"唔好亂講，兩邊都要清算<br />\n愧對嗰句光復香港時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:42:12.000Z","msg":"重點係警犬唔做野大於黑社會<br />\n同默許黑社會一樣<br />\n你有乜野能力打壓黑幫？<br />\n你點樣比黑幫無賴 殺人？<br />\n你做得出好講"},{"pid":"e5fb9949da4880fa6956671b0d1ec9530866fc59","tid":1352740,"uid":266309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:49:24.000Z","msg":"理西佢，<br />\n將佢地綁埋一齊咪可以一次過清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefc001fdf67692e838110ad09b766827954afa5","tid":1352740,"uid":7079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:00:44.000Z","msg":"啱應該要先針對警察<br />\n黑社會搞事係天職<br />\n警察勾結鄉黑係失職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1094a29d9c62324cd77cc5ccf990cddc3037707d","tid":1352740,"uid":130869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:46:10.000Z","msg":"警先係重點 黑幫打人到處都有 但比佢地勇氣既係黑警"},{"pid":"ac2243c6c5ba6a7787402d8c24fdd640f2ed6c74","tid":1352740,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffa41c283c914c60271707c8686413510881a0bb","tid":1352740,"uid":272976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:35:51.000Z","msg":"唔好亂講，兩邊都要清算<br />\n愧對嗰句光復香港時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"清一次牛屎佬，仲有千千萬萬個牛屎佬，我想講嘅係既然狗將調查力當武器，就要諗辦法對抗狗隻嘅調查能力，例如黑衫面罩呢啲都係對抗調查。<br />\n<br />\n但會唔會有方法可以更好解決？咁先可以令整個運動更加順利。<br />\n<br />\n牛屎佬唔會走，牛屎佬幾時清都得，當然我唔反對光復，但係我覺得重點喺狗嗰邊。"},{"pid":"3cd8852ea0eeacb05bb277d0715f535c68bf3aef","tid":1352740,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:04:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"ddd80932c59e7c6fade24e8cfe41c166e2dfa626","tid":1352740,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:08:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"ed85c9937b2f3eecd6fb930251bf2487feacdd5f","tid":1352740,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:10:07.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"28e12c2a4ac74962261210d4da6c30230df39ab1","tid":1352740,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"444fe268b07379b1f3b7a26154947c7c70689ce1","tid":1352740,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:10:44.000Z","msg":"why not both"},{"pid":"134971dd08ae4a446725c7971237cb581de3ebf6","tid":1352740,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:10:55.000Z","msg":"[727光復元朗]  727元朗反黑反恐行動部署提議<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354479</a><br />\n<br />\n727光復元朗 (副題：元朗反黑反恐行動) <br />\n口號：肅清鄉黑，除暴安良 <br />\n目的：以武力震懾元朗鄉黑勢力，保障元朗社區安全。 <br />\n<br />\n727香港人嘅主要目標有 <br />\n1. 針對鄉黑黃賭毒勢力經濟進行破壞 (首要目標：黃色經濟) <br />\n<br />\n大家唔好唔記得除咗元朗有黑社會之外。 <br />\n元朗區同屯門公園一樣，有色情流鶯問題。 <br />\n掃鄉黑圍村個時，幫埋元朗區搞掂埋黃色問題。 <br />\n<br />\n建議： <br />\n進行141洗樓行動，對流鶯進行驅趕。 <br />\n為咗cut班鄉黑嘅收入 <br />\n<br />\n一樓一地址141個網有架啦。我睇下post唔post出嚟 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非都可以係一樓一門口貼下紙仔 <br />\n個人推介可以貼五十路林鄭av封面圖同鄭若驊大波圖係一樓一舊樓門口。 <br />\n<br />\n勇武手足可以注意睇下啲粉紅光管，啲門口cam可以點做。<br />\n<br />\n同埋call埋入境處舉報有人違反逗留條件，入境處都有執法嘅權力。 <br />\n<br />\n舉報違反入境條例罪行 <a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/investigation/onlinereportoffence.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fimmigration%2Finvestigation%2Fonlinereportoffence.htm&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=857d4ceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/investigation/onlinereportoffence.htm</a><br />\n電話：入境事務處24小時舉報熱線： (852) 2824 1551 (舉報後獲提供一個檔案編號) <br />\n<br />\n人地已經ready <br />\n［遍地開花］年輕紀律部隊要爬山 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1354244/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1354244/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n麻雀館大家睇下可以點搞，我唔熟"},{"pid":"e8c9c41e942db6e9406e3cad0d4c0155a142dc6a","tid":1352740,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:10:57.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"c95becd214e50495c11b3591e50029bbc3bb542b","tid":1352740,"uid":39287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:11:16.000Z","msg":"兩邊都要滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455079fea367ac45667d7a2da78105ffd59fc154","tid":1352740,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"444fe268b07379b1f3b7a26154947c7c70689ce1","tid":1352740,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:10:44.000Z","msg":"why not both"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"只係而家啲人淨係掛住班牛屎佬"},{"pid":"bbff703858d3ca92f33d7337ba1804be89c6eeb4","tid":1352740,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c95becd214e50495c11b3591e50029bbc3bb542b","tid":1352740,"uid":39287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:11:16.000Z","msg":"兩邊都要滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b44011d28f28796d3ed88cae4b85dbe9cbf2a6","tid":1352740,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"455079fea367ac45667d7a2da78105ffd59fc154","tid":1352740,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"444fe268b07379b1f3b7a26154947c7c70689ce1","tid":1352740,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:10:44.000Z","msg":"why not both"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"只係而家啲人淨係掛住班牛屎佬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"牛屎易搞，警察難"},{"pid":"81311532a7cb3e720ec1f17cfd77734ef822ff8a","tid":1352740,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7b44011d28f28796d3ed88cae4b85dbe9cbf2a6","tid":1352740,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"455079fea367ac45667d7a2da78105ffd59fc154","tid":1352740,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"444fe268b07379b1f3b7a26154947c7c70689ce1","tid":1352740,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:10:44.000Z","msg":"why not both"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"只係而家啲人淨係掛住班牛屎佬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"牛屎易搞，警察難"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:13:27.000Z","msg":"都係嘅，但係攔路狗後面就係政府，點都要對付。"},{"p